Espace Real Estate is pleased to present this immaculate example of a type 3E property in the sought-after community of Al Reem. The ground floor comprises a large open plan living and dining area, a study which can be used as a downstairs guest bedroom, a powder room which has been converted to a full bathroom and a closed, modern, upgraded kitchen. This property benefits from a bigger living area than most 3Es, as the wall has been moved towards the kitchen. The first floor consists of a family bathroom and three large bedrooms with built-in storage space, including the master which further benefits from an additional en-suite bathroom and balcony overlooking the private pool and park.
